Privacy Policy

Daniel Duvanå built the MonsterMaker app as a free app. This service is provided by Daniel Duvanå at no cost and is intended for use as is.

MonsterMaker collects data on player interactions such as what is being drawn and what drawing settings are most used (such as colors and brush sizes).
No data is ever handed over to third-parties. The data is used soley for administrating the game and for evaluating how to improve the game.

Contact Me

If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at email: daniel.b.olofsson@gmail.com.
